text: Albert Neumann (19 October 1899 - 1 March 1976) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1899 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Troisvierges
